36:41.680 --> 36:42.640
I want to help you.

36:44.640 --> 36:45.600
Yes.

36:47.600 --> 36:48.800
How tailor-made.

36:51.440 --> 36:52.400
How do I look?

36:53.480 --> 36:54.440
Perfect.

