Angus, Linda.

37:01.040 --> 37:02.480
Linda, Angus.

37:02.600 --> 37:03.920
Hi.  Nice to meet you.

37:04.320 --> 37:05.280
You are his...

37:05.520 --> 37:06.480
I am his stepmother.

37:06.600 --> 37:07.560
No she is not.

37:08.920 --> 37:12.440
She is... was my
father's girlfriend.

37:12.560 --> 37:13.520
Does not make a difference.

37:14.320 --> 37:16.200
