waitress on the tap?

37:38.440 --> 37:40.520
Yeah, showing her
bum with every pothole?

37:41.840 --> 37:42.800
They still exist.

37:47.840 --> 37:49.280
I loved that thing.

37:50.600 --> 37:53.240
He purposely drove into
holes to make me laugh.

38:08.800 --> 38:09.760
There they are.

38:12.520 --> 38:13.880
We will make peace.

38:14.520 --> 38:15.680
You're kidding, aren't you?

38:31.880 --> 38:33.800
I was in extreme panic today.

38:36.400 --> 38:37.400
But that seemed different.

38:40.120 --> 38:41.080
We can be strong

38:41.400 --> 38:43.200
and be scared at
the same time, right?

38:49.320 --> 38:50.680
This is our job.

38:55.680 --> 38:56.760
Strong women.

39:01.280 --> 39:02.240
To Jackie.

39:03.840 --> 39:04.800
To Jackie.

39:10.840 --> 39:11.800
Oh my God.

39:25.880 --> 39:27.840
We are the reason
the boy was shot.

39:28.600 --> 39:30.600
We're the reason
he had a chance.

39:32.360 --> 39:33.320
Had we left him there, he would

39:33.440 --> 39:34.640
have been dead in 30 minutes.

39:34.800 --> 39:36.320
