No.

39:40.800 --> 39:41.760
That’s not going well.

39:42.640 --> 39:44.400
That's why we're drinking this...

39:45.200 --> 39:46.920
...here and now.

39:47.640 --> 39:48.600
Did you steal that?

39:48.960 --> 39:50.160
It was a gift from Volkov.

39:52.200 --> 39:53.280
To the salvation of the world.

40:01.600 --> 40:04.040
You beat the captain of a
Russian submarine today.

40:05.240 --> 40:06.200
He deserves it.

40:07.680 --> 40:08.680
Yes that's true.

40:13.600 --> 40:15.520
Now you understand why I
stood before the court-martial.

40:18.120 --> 40:19.360
Sometimes they just deserve it.
